articles.title: Mark Zuckerberg Reportedly Met With Trump at Mar-a-Lago - Business Insider
articles.description: Meta CEO Mark Zuckerberg met with Trump. Meta confirmed the dinner, saying, "it's an important time for the future of American Innovation."
articles.content:
Mark Zuckerberg became the latest tech CEO to meet with President-elect Donald Trump.
